      <title>亚洲寻求购买更多美国化石燃料以取悦特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/asia-looks-to-buy-more-us-fossil-fuels-to-make-trump-happy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了安抚即将上任的美国总统唐纳德·特朗普，亚洲化石燃料买家得出了同样的结论：购买更多美国石油和天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/asia-looks-to-buy-more-us-fossil-fuels-to-make-trump-happy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 02:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国议员警告称，里夫斯的成本节约计划可能失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-lawmakers-warn-reeves-cost-savings-drive-may-fall-flat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国议员对财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）削减浪费性支出的计划表示质疑，并警告说，新成立的效率部门人手不足，没有时间完成其职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-lawmakers-warn-reeves-cost-savings-drive-may-fall-flat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国面临特朗普关税威胁 准备应对“所有情况”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-facing-threat-of-trump-tariffs-braces-for-all-scenarios</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国总统职位于周一易主，新一任唐纳德·特朗普政府威胁要对与世界其他国家的贸易征收关税，英国首相基尔·斯塔默正在为所有可能发生的情况做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-facing-threat-of-trump-tariffs-braces-for-all-scenarios</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
